data.description: Gorgeously updated home in quiet neighborhood zoned to Klein ISD! Easily access I45 & 99 for your daily commute. This stunning 3 bed 2 bath home is complete w/ new flooring, fresh paint, resurfaced fireplace, updated sinks & faucets throughout, updated appliances in kitchen, & new roof. Enjoy entertaining your family & friends on the lrg covered patio & beautifully landscaped yard. The open concept living allows for organic flow throughout & adds the utmost in comfort! *Close to New Exxon Campus
